---
title: Cheesy Plant-Based Mince & Bacon Loaded Fries with Creamy Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Get your loaded fries with cheesy plant-based mince and crispy nuggets of bacon right here, right now! We’ve got a side of creamy, crunchy slaw and a sprinkle of spring onions for extra flair when you cook up these loaded fries tonight.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67a1a74f9c4cafbaaa040fe4-cf842d2d.jpeg
